org.apache.flink.contrib.tweetinputformat.model.User

类 Users

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.contrib.tweetinputformat.model.User.Users

  • public class Users
extends Object
    Users can be anyone or anything. They Tweet , follow, create lists, have a home_timeline, can be mentioned, and can be looked up in bulk.
